<p>Please quote the reviews and presentations published on <i>recensio.net</i> in the following way:</p>
<ul>
<li>author of contribution</li>
<li>title of contribution</li>
<li>volume and number of the quoted journal issue</li>
<li>number of quoted paragraph (e.g.: &lt;4&gt;) or page numbers</li>
<li>exact online address (URL = universal resource locator) and URN      (uniform resource name)</li>
<li>date when you consulted the text</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
<p>Please quote comments by putting the commentator’s name in front of the above-mentioned information, marked with the note »comment on«.</p>
<p> </p>
<p>You can find document-specific citation rules on the front page of every recallable pdf-file and accordingly at the bottom end of every text supplied in html.</p>